r avenue eontario ohownership privateamtrustnorthamericaamtrustnabeta descriptionamtrust financial services inc was founded in  to provide property and casualty insurance to small businesses in addition to being the nations th largest insurer of workers compensation amtrust is also a substantial writer of community banks their financial institutions team has over  years average industry experience insuring community banks and currently writes over  banks nationwideproductsspecialty coverage insuranceon march   excess deposit bond  a costeffective means to provide depositors with coverage that is over and above the k provided by the fdic civil money penalties personal protection  covers the institutionaffiliated party in the event civil money penalties are assessed against that individual by a regulatory agency – an exposure no longer covered by a bank’s management liability policy eft guard – also known as “corporate account takeover coverage” and protects a financial institution’s business banking customers for losses stemming from fraudulent ach and wire transfers perpetrated through the customer’s system and outside of the financial institution professional lines insuranceon march   directors  officers – provides a b and c coverage with additional m aside specifically for bank directors  officers lender liability  “broad form” coverage extends to suits brought by other persons or entities that may be damaged as a result of the lending or foreclosure process professional services liability covers claims due to errors or omissions involving professional services trust liability  covers claims due to errors or omissions involving trust services employment practices liability covers claims for actual or alleged wrongful acts such as discrimination sexual harassment and other employmentrelated causes of action fiduciary liability  covers claims for errors or omissions or negligent acts with respect to the administration of an employee benefit plan or breach of fiduciary duty or responsibilities imposed by erisa cobra hipaa or similar laws cyber liability  protects the insured against losses for the failure to protect a customer’s information ssn credit card numbers medical information passwords etc via theft unauthorized access viruses or denial of service attack  includes media liability regulatory defense crisis mitigation cyber extortion and business interruption coverage financial institution bond  provides the fidelity coverage required by regulators and covers various types of fraud exposures financial institutions inevitably face while doing business in the st century property  casualty insuranceon march   property  covers bank properties as well as building and tenant glass attached and detached signage with no persign limitation antennas and satellite dishes vaults and atms and electronic data processing general liability  includes limits for bodily injury property damage personal and advertising injury commercial auto  ability to write on an owned auto or hirednonowned only basis workers compensation  can coordinate with the general liability for employers liability in monopolistic states umbrella  available limits up to  million foreclosed property – ability to write foreclosures on a reporting form or individual basis forceplaced property – basic and special forms available amtrust financial services inc adds new warranty products and customers with the acquisition of tmi solutions llc  thestreet action alerts plus access aapjim cramers best stocks for charitable trust portfoliomost recent trade alert investing rules trading commandments real money access rm rules of investingjim cramers best stocks for  commandmentsstressed out stockscramers blog cramer mad money etfs futures markets much more banksbiotechretailtechpersonal financeretirementfinancial advisor centerhow to spendoptionsfixed incomevideo privacy policyterms of use  thestreet inc all rights reserved djia nasdaq sp  market data updated sign in your member